THE TIME IS NOW: Shedding Pain and Embracing the Shift

December 16, 2024

 

As the Pope opens the door of the Vatican, a symbolic act with profound spiritual significance, a battle within the spiritual realms becomes more visible here on Earth. What was once hidden is surfacing, and the energy of this transition is noticeable. This shift marks a turning point. A time where light begins to overrule darkness, and the truths long buried rise to the surface.

We are entering a period of transformation. The ways of the past, built on deception, greed, and control, can no longer exist. Humanity is being called to awaken, to shed the dense energy of pain and trauma that has weighed us down for generations. This energy, born of our unresolved wounds and unprocessed emotions, has fueled forces that thrive on division, fear, and chaos. But now, as the tide turns, it is up to each of us to release these burdens and step into a higher state of being.

The Spiritual Battle Within and Around Us

This is not just a physical or external shift. It is a spiritual one. The energy of the world is changing, and with it comes a heightened awareness of the battle between light and dark. The spiritual realms are stirring, and the veil between them and our physical reality is thinning. This can feel overwhelming, as many dark truths about the systems and structures we have trusted will come to light.

But remember: the light has already won. Those who have sought to control and manipulate are witnessing their own downfall. Their power was rooted in our collective disconnection. Our disconnection from ourselves, each other, and the truth. The more we let go of our pain, traumas, and dense energy, the less power these forces have over us.

Letting Go to Step Into the Light

Letting go does not mean forgetting or ignoring what has happened to you. It means acknowledging your pain, understanding its impact, and consciously choosing to release its hold on your energy. Pain and trauma are heavy. They dim your inner light and keep you suck in the past. When you let go, you reclaim your energy and your power, making space for healing, growth, and clarity.

This shift requires courage. As dark truths come to the forefront, you will be challenged to confront not only the lies of the external world but also the ones you have told yourself. It’s a time to break free from the illusions that have kept you small, fearful, or stuck.

The time is now to ask yourself:

  • What pain am I still holding onto?
  • What traumas have I allowed to define me?
  • Am I ready to release these and embrace the light within me?

A New Era of Truth

As this transition unfolds, the world will feel chaotic. Structures that once seemed immovable will crumble. Institutions we believed in may reveal their true nature. This upheaval is not something to fear. It is a necessary part of clearing the way for a new era of truth, connection, and unity.

You may feel the weight of this change in your own life. Old habits, relationships, and ways of thinking that no longer serve you will start to fall away. This is the natural process of evolution. By releasing what no longer aligns, you create space for what does.

Remember: you are not powerless. You have the ability to choose how you navigate this shift. You can let go of the dense energy that keeps you stuck and step into a higher vibration. You can tune into the truth within yourself, rather than relying on external sources to define it for you.

The Power of Awareness

This is a time for awakening, and it starts with awareness. The truth is not something someone else can hand to you. It is something you must seek and feel within yourself. Trust your intuition, strengthen your connection to your inner guidance, and allow yourself to evolve.

Good will prevail, but the journey requires each of us to do our part. By shedding the pain and traumas of the past, we lighten our energy and contribute to the collective shift. We become beacons of light, helping to illuminate the path for others.

The Choice Is Yours

The battle between light and dark is reaching its climax, but the outcome has already been decided. The light has won, and now it is time for you to step into your role in this transformation. You are being called to let go, to heal, and to rise.

The time is now to reclaim your energy, seek the truth, and become the person you were always meant to be. The choice is yours. Will you hold onto the ways of the past, or will you embrace the shift and step into the light of the future?

The door has been opened. 

The truth is ready to be revealed. 

It is time to walk through and see the world, 

and yourself for what you truly are.


hunter johnson
